10	[{"value": "<ul><li><h4>Tour snapshot</h4><p>Tap into local culture in Los Angeles! Join us for\\u00a0an orientation tour\\u00a0of Hollywood.\\u00a0Hang out with\\u00a0an in-the-know local\\u00a0who can\\u00a0introduce you to the city\\u00a0and tell you what to do, where to go, and how to make the most of your time\\u00a0in\\u00a0LA.\\u00a0\\u00a0</p></li><li><h4>Highlights</h4><ul><li>Chat with a Los Angeles-based local expert who can help you plan your Best. Days. Ever. while you\\u2019re in town</li><li>Learn all the secret local tips you won\\u2019t find in most guidebooks</li><li>Meet up with fellow like-minded travellers</li><li>Take a mini tour of Hollywood</li><li>Kick back with new friends at a funky spot in a great neighbourhood</li></ul></li><p>Inclusions: Local English-speaking expert to answer all your questions.</p><p>Exclusions: Transportation to and from the meet-up point, food and drinks.</p></ul>", "type": "paragraph"}]	15	00:00:00	30	12
20	[{"value": "<p>Get picked up at your hotel for a private 4 hour sightseeing tour of the Ancient Bagan, Irraweddy river, and perhaps a couple of other beautiful places along the way.</p>", "type": "paragraph"}]	35	04:00:00	11	14
23	[{"value": "<p>On this Yangon walking tour, your guide will give you an orientation of the neighbourhood that includes places most visitors never see, and stop by several shops where you can purchase local foods to try.</p>", "type": "paragraph"}]	65	06:00:00	31	18
24	[{"value": "<p>Ever plan a whole elaborate Inlay shebang just to come back with blurry photos taken at sweaty clubs? Document your special outing or have a fun photo shoot in style with Kyaw Kyaw and his crew. He'll take you on a photo shoot tour of some of the most scenic locations in Inle. A long-time resident of Taungyi, he can even give you pointers and tips for the rest of your trip for both on Inle and Taungyi.</p><p>Package also includes photo retouching, an online gallery &amp; instant digital download of the high resolution images with a usage &amp; copyright release.</p>", "type": "paragraph"}]	64	05:00:00	36	12
6	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h4><br/></h4><h4>Tour snapshot</h4><ul><li>Greet the day the local way! Grab a local-style breakfast, then go for a market wander, see a few temples, and enjoy a tasty lunch on this all-in-one food-meets-culture Mandalay.\\u00a0<br/></li></ul><h4>Highlights</h4><ul><li>Experience local life in Mandalay in the tastiest way: through its food!<br/></li><li>Wander the city\\u2019s vibrant morning markets, including the Zaycho and Mingalar markets.<br/></li><li>Enjoy an authentic Burmese breakfast and lunch with local dishes like <em>kyae oh\\u00a0</em>\\u00a0and <i>moh hin ga.</i><br/></li><li>Explore the palace, the last Burmese king lived.</li></ul><ul><p>Inclusions: Local English-speaking guide, breakfast and lunch, coffee break, entrance fees, transportation.\\u00a0</p><p>Exclusions: Additional food and drink, souvenirs and items of a personal nature, tips/gratuities for drivers and guide.\\u00a0</p></ul>"}]	63	04:30:00	11	8
25	[{"value": "<p>Get ready to witness the best-of-the-best as your excursion begins with a journey past Irraweddy.</p>", "type": "paragraph"}]	62	04:00:00	34	14
21	[{"value": "<p>Yes, it is just as romantic as it sounds!</p><p>Escape the crowds of Yangon and enjoy one of Ngwesaung's spectacular sunsets with amazing views of the bay of Bangal from the water. Spend 2 hours on your own private yacht- a romantic sail for 2 or up to a group of 6.</p><p>BYOB.</p>", "type": "paragraph"}]	67	04:30:00	35	16
22	[{"value": "<p>Once the Kingdom, Mandalay is now known as the largest street art gallery in the Myanmar! Made famous by the yearly art fair, the Mandalay area has exploded into one of the hippest neighborhoods in the country. From wheat pastes to murals, stencils to stickers, every inch of the neighborhood is covered in art. This walking tour of the neighborhood will include information about the street art coupled with the history of the neighborhood, the ins-and-outs of the current changes, and the way that Mandalay fits into the overall picture of Myanmar. I can give tours in both English and French, and I can arrange for bike rentals for an additional fee. Come and check out Mandalay's street art hub!</p>", "type": "paragraph"}]	66	00:00:00	28	8
26	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<ul><li><p>Uncover the astounding mix of nationalities that make up the City of Mawlamyine on this Mawlamyine food tour that reveals hole-in-the-wall eateries, markets, snack shops.</p></li></ul>"}, {"type": "image", "value": {"style": "contain", "image": 37, "caption": ""}}, {"type": "image", "value": {"style": "contain", "image": 38, "caption": ""}}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<ul><li><h4>Highlights</h4><ul><li>Taste sweet and savory foods from Chinatown.</li><li>Experience the culture and learn the history of these diverse neighborhoods</li><li>Admire ornate historic architecture and get a glimpse of the bay of Bangal.</li></ul></li><p>Inclusions: Select sweet and savory tastings (vegetarian options available with\\u00a0advance notice upon booking); Some drinks (non-alcoholic) and water;\\u00a0 English speaking local guide.</p><p>Notes: Please indicate vegetarian preferences or any dietary restrictions upon booking. We will do our best to accommodate them although we cannot guarantee an alternative option at each stop.</p><p>Exclusions: Additional food and drink items, return transportation to start point, tips / gratuities for your guide</p></ul>"}, {"type": "embed", "value": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bgrLAaD5niI"}]	61	05:00:00	11	15
42	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h4>Tour Snapshot</h4><p>A fun packed tour for some of the most amazing sites in Yangon. Will learn the local way of life, eat the local food and shopping at Bogyoke market.</p><h4>Highlights<br/></h4><p></p><p></p><ul><li>Amazing view of Sule pagoda.</li><li>Photo ops with Yangon City Hall and colonial buildings.</li><li>Cross river with Yangon Jetty see some of Myanmar people's way of life</li><li>Sacred site of Chaukhtgyi pagoda.</li><li>Shopping at Bogyoke market, one of the tourist attractions in the city of Yangon.</li><li>Sunset view at the great Shwedagon pagoda.</li></ul><p></p><p></p><h4>What's included</h4><p>Local english-speaking guide, transportation and entrance fees.</p><h5>What's Not included</h5><p>Food and drink, souvenirs and items of a personal nature, tips/gratuities for drivers and guide.\\u00a0<br/></p>"}]	79	12:00:00	41	18
